{"article_id":"4FQUIQKV3SUONl3s","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Virginia Democratic Gov . Ralph Northam apologized Friday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"for appearing in a \" racist and offensive \" photo on his 1984 medical school yearbook page","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that showed one man","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"dressed in blackface and another in a KKK robe ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"while giving no indication","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"he plans to resign .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Northam","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"who has been under fire this week for comments","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"made about a third-trimester abortion bill in his state -","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"admitted to being one of the people in the photo ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"though it ' s not clear which costume he is wearing .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"\" Earlier today , a website published a photograph of me from my 1984 medical school yearbook in a costume","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that is clearly racist and offensive , \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Northam said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"He added ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"\" I am deeply sorry for the decision","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"I made","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"to appear","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"as I did in this photo","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"and for the hurt","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that decision caused then and now . \"","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Turning to Twitter on Friday night","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"to speak directly with the public ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"he elaborated on his error in judgment , and on his apology for it ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"the photo does n't reflect the person","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"he is today","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"or how he 's conducted himself as a public servant .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"In a video","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"accompanying his tweet ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"he said ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"`` I can not change the decisions","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"I made ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"nor can I undo the harm","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"my behavior caused then and today . ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"he was committed to continuing his work as governor","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"and `` living up to the expectations","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"you set for me . ''","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Fox News obtained a copy of the 1984 yearbook page from the Eastern Virginia Medical School library .","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"Northam graduated from the school that year .","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"The Virginian-Pilot , the Washington Post and the Richmond Times-Dispatch also reported","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"they independently confirmed the authenticity of the page .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"The quote on the page says ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"\" There are more old drunks than old doctors in this world","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"so I think","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"I ' ll have another beer . \"","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"VIRGINIA GOV . NORTHAM FACES BACKLASH FOR COMMENTS ON 3RD-TRIMESTER ABORTION BILL","depth":2},{"id":49,"text":"A growing number of both Republicans and Democrats on Friday evening said","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Northam should step down .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"\" Racism has no place in Virginia , \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Republican Party of Virginia chairman Jack Wilson said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"\" These pictures are wholly inappropriate .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"If Gov . Northam appeared in blackface or dressed in a KKK robe ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"he should resign immediately . \"","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Derrick Johnson , the leader of the NAACP , also called for Northam 's resignation ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"as did Democratic presidential candidate Julian Castro .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"`` If @ RalphNortham is one of the two people","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"pictured in the highly disturbing , horrific photo","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"wearing either blackface or a KKK hood","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"- or if he selected or approved of its use on his yearbook page -","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"he should immediately resign , ''","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"the liberal MoveOn.org group tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"`` There are no excuses for such a racist display . ''","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Northam did not respond to those calls .","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"But in his statement , he said ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"`` This behavior is not in keeping with who I am today","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"and the values","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"I have fought for throughout my career in the military , in medicine , and in public service . ''","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" I recognize","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"that it will take time and serious effort to heal the damage","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"this conduct has caused , ''","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Northam said .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"`` I am ready to do that important work .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"The first step is to offer my sincerest apology","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"and to state my absolute commitment","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"to living up to the expectations","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Virginians set for me","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"when they elected me to be their governor . \"","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"Earlier on Friday , a conservative website","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"called Big League Politics","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"first posted a photo of the yearbook page .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"The White House took aim at Northam ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"referencing the attention","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Supreme Court Justice Brett Kavanaugh 's high school yearbook received during his brutal confirmation fight last year .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"`` This should be easier work","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"than parsing every word and semicolon in the Kavanaugh yearbook , ''","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"White House adviser Kellyanne Conway tweeted Friday .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"The newest revelation comes","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"as Northam came under fire Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"after he waded into the fight over a controversial abortion bill","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"one sponsor said","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"could allow women to terminate a pregnancy up until the moment before birth","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"-- with critics saying","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"Northam indicated","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"a child could be killed after birth .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Northam ' s troubles began Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"when he appeared on WTOP","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"to discuss The Repeal Act .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Northam , a former pediatric neurologist , was asked about the sponsor 's comments","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"he couldn ' t speak for Tran ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"but said","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that third-trimester abortions are done with \" the consent of obviously the mother , with consent of the physician , multiple physicians by the way ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"and it ' s done in cases","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"where there may be severe deformities","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"or there may be a fetus","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"that ' s not viable . \"","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"\" So in this particular example","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"if a mother is in labor ,","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"I can tell you exactly what would happen ,","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"the infant would be delivered , \"","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"Northam said .","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"\" The infant would be kept comfortable .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"The infant would be resuscitated","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"if that ' s what the mother and the family desired ,","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"and then a discussion would ensue between the physicians and the mother . \"","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"The intent of his comments was not clear .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"But some conservative commentators and lawmakers took his remarks to mean","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"he was discussing the possibility","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"of letting a newborn die","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"-- or even `` infanticide . ''","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"Northam refused to back down from comments","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"that have sparked outrage .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"`` I have devoted my life to caring for children","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"and any insinuation otherwise is shameful and disgusting , ''","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Northam tweeted this week .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"\" What ' s shameful is that you 're too cowardly","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"to say point blank","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"that it ' s wrong to leave babies to die after birth , \"","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"Nebraska Sen. Ben Sasse said in a statement Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"\" You could have said that yesterday .","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"because you ' re terrified of an extremist pro-abortion lobby","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"that now defends even infanticide ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"you 're still ducking . ''","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Northam defeated Republican Ed Gillespie in Virginia ' s 2017 gubernatorial race .","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"During that contest , Democrats tried to link Gillespie to the torch-bearing white nationalists","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"who infamously marched in Charlottesville .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"When he won ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"California Sen. Kamala Harris tweeted congratulations to Northam","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"for `` showing","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"that Virginia won ' t stand for hatred and bigotry . ''","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Last month , Florida 's secretary of state resigned","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"after a local newspaper obtained photos of him","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"dressed in blackface as a Hurricane Katrina victim .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":295,"left":195,"right":294,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":187,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":169,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":153,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":151,"right":152,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":0,"right":150,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":1,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":158,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":157,"right":11,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":156,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":6,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":7,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":160,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":159,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nucleari